'''Wuta''' was an [[Ewok/Legends|Ewok]] [[Gender/Legends|male]] scout on the [[Endor/Legends|forest moon]] of [[Endor (planet)/Legends|Endor]]. He tracked predators and searched for fallen trees to make tools. He was the first Ewok to notice the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] when they began establishing a presence on Endor.<ref name="CCG">{{CCG|set=Endor Limited|cardname=Wuta}}</ref> He shares his name with a [[Wuta (spirit)|spirit]] in Ewok mythology.<ref name="GCG">''[[Galactic Campaign Guide]]''</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
Although the image of Wuta in [[Star Wars Insider 135|''Star Wars Insider'' 135]] depicts him in a hood with the stitching on the right side of his head<ref name="SWI 135">{{InsiderCite|135|Rogues Gallery|Rogues Gallery: The Ewoks: Warriors of Endor!}}</ref>, his Decipher card image shows the stitching at the center.<ref name="CCG" />

